      "date": "2017-01-12 11:02:49.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> I was going to put the --list-commands implementation into a\n > separate patch to reduce the size of the changes.  Would you prefer\n > that I include the --list-commands change with this patch?\n\nSince the error messages are referencing that command, if you want to put it into a separate patch it should precede this one, or the references to the command should be removed from this patch until --list-commands is available.",
